Opinion 'I FORGIVE HIM' Teen ‘rape victim’ who was ‘dumped in her front yard to freeze to death’ by high school footballers speaks out about horrific ordeal 
Daisy Coleman, from Missouri, US, was just 14 when she was attacked, along with her 13-year-old friend Paige Parkhurst Video By Zoe Nauman US Online Reporter 3rd February 2017, 12:27 am
